      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get that there are social issues, but what about the people who actually live in high crime areas? they usually want more police and stricter punishments so they can feel safe in their own homes. isn't saying that \"tough on crime\" is bad basically ignoring the need for public safety and deterrence?",
